      "summary": "The SimpleCard component provides a versatile, multi-format card structure for displaying basic information such as title, description, and date. Its primary purpose is to serve as a lightweight, customizable card that can be rendered in various formats—including isolated, embedded, fitted, badge, strip, tile, and full card layouts—adaptable to different container sizes and contexts. The component emphasizes clarity and flexibility in presenting foundational data with consistent styling and optional iconography.",
